high_descs: Move over to the left side of the cabinet with the coffee maker on top.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the tomato.
Look up at the potato to the left of the coffee maker.
Cut the potato on the left of the coffee maker.
Turn left and go to the white table.
Put the knife on the table to the left of the lettuce.
Turn right and go back to the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left, go across the room, turn right and head to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave and pick the slice of potato back up.
Turn right, go across the room and then turn left to face the trash can.
Put the slice of potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the trash can.

high_descs: Step forward to face the table the coffee maker is on.
Pick up the spoon on the left side of the table.
Look up to face the potato on the back of the table.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Take a step to the left to face the white table.
Place the knife on the table next to the lettuce.
Step to the right to face the potato on the table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn left to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the potato slice in the trash can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: To heat slice of potato and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn and face the small table
Pick up a butterknife from the table
Face the potato on the table
Cut the potato on the table
Go to the white table
Place the butterknife down on the table
Go to the small table with the cut potato
Pick up a potato slice from the table
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice in the microwave
Go to the trash bin
Place the heated potato slice in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato slice in a trash bin
